INSERT INTO `locations` VALUES (8,'Apiary - Menara Global','http://apiary.id/','0818165222','Menara Global 15th Floor Unit C-D, Jl. Gatot Subroto No.Kav. 27, RT.3/RW.3, Kuningan, Kuningan Tim., Kuningan, Kota Jakarta Selatan, Daerah Khusus Ibukota Jakarta 12950','https://goo.gl/maps/SqRtgYfZxjeFAqc39','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15864.975806776843!2d106.8214536!3d-6.231537!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x275e5e1788209e5f!2sApiary%20Coworking%20Space%20(Kuningan)!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1579084936090!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Located in the bustling heart of Jakarta, Apiary is now offering coworking space in Kuningan.\nIf you are looking for an event space, meeting room, private office, shared desk or serviced office in Kuningan, South Jakarta, you are welcome to the hospitality of our community here in Apiary Coworking Space. Equipped with printer, free flow coffee, tea and other beverages, projector, sound system, locker space, daily events and more.','2020-01-15 19:13:02','2020-01-15 19:13:02','apiary-menara-global','Jakarta Selatan','hello@apiary.id','Coworking Space'),(9,'Apiary St. Moritz','http://apiary.id/','0818165222','Unit 901, Apiary Coworking Space Lippo St. Moritz Office Tower (Floor 9, Jl. Kedoya Duri Jl. Puri Indah Raya, South Kembangan, Kembangan, Jakarta Barat 11610','https://goo.gl/maps/kqmdA57BDqsFCXyZA','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15866.282542963312!2d106.7385744!3d-6.188167!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xac82f0de284b152a!2sApiary%20Coworking%20Space%20(Puri)!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1579084191041!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Situated under a well-built architecture and high security building, where Apiary is strategically located.\nNext to an upbeat coffee & brunch presence, and just right beside the mall. All comes in one perfectly for your everyday work & commuting stress relief.','2020-01-15 19:20:49','2020-01-15 19:20:49','apiary-st-moritz','Jakarta Barat','hello@apiary.id','Coworking Space'),(10,'Arkamaya','https://www.arkamayaculinary.com/','08119233777','Jl. Jend Gatot Subroto Kav. 51-52, Ruko A9 Petamburan, Slipi Jakarta Pusat – 10260','https://goo.gl/maps/AivLw2fVQYtTYKQcA','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15865.85364913405!2d106.8006901!3d-6.2024351!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xd99ba33e252e129c!2sArkamaya%20Indonesian%20CREATIVE%20Culinary%20Education!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1579085658643!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Inspired by the food industry that keeps developing as fast as poaching an egg, Arkamaya offers a first-class culinary education of Indonesian cuisine in the heart of Jakarta.\nIt is our belief that everyone has that creative soul and hunger for greatness. Accordingly, we have built a diverse range of programs (academy and short courses) for every person fond of Indonesian food, either a professional or an everyday learner. Each lesson will simmer your creativity to take that familiar taste from your mother’s kitchen, mix it well, and turn it into something new.','2020-01-15 19:24:44','2020-01-15 19:24:44','arkamaya','Jakarta Pusat','info@arkamayaculinary.com','Cooking & Baking Studio'),(11,'GoWork Pondok Indah','https://go-work.com/pondok-indah--jakarta-selatan','08119968896','Pondok Indah Office Tower 2, 15th Floor Jl. Sultan Iskandar Muda Kav. VTA, Pondok Indah, Jakarta Selatan 12310','https://g.page/GoWorkPondokIndah?share','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15864.046792913354!2d106.781982!3d-6.2621886!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xb75614793d0773b2!2sGoWork%20Pondok%20Indah%20-%20Coworking%20and%20Office%20Space!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1579088099151!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','This coworking space puts you exactly in one of Jakarta’s chicest area, Pondok Indah. Located on the 15th floor of Pondok Indah Office Tower 2 gives you convenient access to one of Jakarta’s most visited mall, Pondok Indah Mall. Besides coming with all the bells and whistles standard of any GoWork locations, GoWork Pondok Indah also offers an accessibility to lots of hubs like none other in around the Pondok Indah area.','2020-01-15 19:29:49','2020-01-15 19:29:49','gowork-pondok-indah','Jakarta Selatan','sales@go-work.com','Coworking Space'),(12,'Sweet Troops','https://sweettroops.com/','085945912722','Jl. Teuku Nyak Arief Blok G no: 16 RT/RW 007/003 Kel. Grogol Selatan Kec. Kebayoran Lama. Jakarta Selatan, DKI Jakarta 12220, Indonesia','https://goo.gl/maps/63qPwY3kVsRyfR4p8','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15864.9693515461!2d106.7886037!3d-6.2317505!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x8364205b4079fa30!2sSweet%20Troops!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1579086209478!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Welcome to Sweet Troops Artisan Baking Studio.  Established in 2016 by Livianca Venaessa.\nOur beautiful baking studio offers hands on pastry classes ranging from baking to decorating workshops specially crafted for all level of learners. Focusing on professional as well as enjoyable class atmosphere, conducted by local and international tutors will ensure the students to get qualified learning experiences.\nWe cannot wait to cake away with you soon!','2020-01-15 19:44:30','2020-01-15 19:44:30','sweet-troops','Jakarta Selatan','st.bakingstudio.rental@gmail.com','Baking Studio');
